text:
Sandrine Doucet (10 September 1959 – 4 February 2019) was a French politician. She was a member of the Socialist Party. Doucet was a Deputy between 2012 and 2017 representing Gironde's 1st constituency. Doucet did not seek re-election in 2017.
Doucet died of cancer at age 59 on 4 February 2019.
